_:N32612d6285694a548a4e0fa54eed127c <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Catherine McKinnell was previously Minister of State (Minister for School Standards) at the Department for Education between 8 July 2024 and 6 September 2025.</p>\n\n<p>She was elected as the Labour MP for Newcastle Upon Tyne North in May 2010.</p>\n" .
